K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-8: // de zad nas phyis kyang gang gis sdig pa'i sgo rnams bcad pa'i mi rnams su de skye'o //
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-9: skyes nas kyang mchog tu gzhon sha chags pa dang /
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-11: lang tsho phul du phyin pa dang /
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-12: 'byor cing yang yul ljongs la dbang bar 'gyur ro //
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-13: gang dag rgyun du zhugs pa ma yin pa de
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-14: dag rnams ni tshe 'phos nas ji ltar chos rnams
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-15: kyis nye bar 'gro bar 'gyur ba dmyal ba dang
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-18: de dag rnams nas 'phos nas gal te yang mi
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-19: rnams dang skal ba mtshungs pa mir skyes na yang
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-20: de rnams de bzhin du gzhon sha can du 'gyur
K10D0287-2_H0289-2:478a-21: zhing rgyan dang cha lugs la mchog tu dga' bar
